\c 27
\s Umfanekiso wamajogwe
\p
\v 1 Ekuqaleni kokubusa\x + 26.1.\x* kukaJehoyakhimi indodana kaJosiya, inkosi yakoJuda,\x + 27.3,12,20; 28.1.\x* kwafika lelilizwi kuJeremiya livela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lisithi:
\v 2 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* kimi: Zenzele imichilo\x + 13.2. 1 Kho. 22.11. Hez. 7.23.\x* lamajogwe,\x + 28.10,12,13. Hez. 30.18; 34.27. Levi 26.13. Isa. 58.6,9.\x* ukugaxe entanyeni yakho,
\v 3 ukuthumele enkosini yeEdoma\x + 25.21,22.\x* lenkosini yakoMowabi\x + 25.21,22.\x* lenkosini yabantwana bakoAmoni\x + 25.21,22.\x* lenkosini yeTire\x + 25.21,22.\x* lenkosini yeSidoni,\x + 25.21,22.\x* ngesandla sezithunywa ezifika eJerusalema kuZedekhiya inkosi yakoJuda;\x + 27.3,12,20; 28.1.\x*
\v 4 uzilaye ukuthi zithi emakhosini azo: Itsho njalo N\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Lizakutsho njalo emakhosini enu:
\v 5 Mina ngenze umhlaba,\x + Isa. 45.12. Hlab. 115.15.\x* umuntu, lenyamazana, okuphezu kobuso bomhlaba, ngamandla ami amakhulu langengalo yami eyeluliweyo,\x + 21.5.\x* ngiwunike lowo okuqondileyo emehlweni ami.\x + Hlab. 115.16. Dan. 4.17,25,32.\x*
\v 6 Khathesi mina sengiwanikele wonke lamazwe esandleni sikaNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni inceku yami;\x + 25.9.\x* njalo ngimnikile lenyamazana zeganga ukuthi zimsebenzele.\x + 28.14. Dan. 2.38.\x*
\v 7 Lezizwe zonke zizasebenzela yena,\x + 2 Lan. 36.20.\x* lendodana yakhe,\x + 52.31.\x* lendodana yendodana yakhe,\x + Dan. 5.1,30.\x* kuze kufike isikhathi selakhe ilizwe uqobo;\x + 2 Lan. 36.20.\x*\x + 25.12.\x* khona izizwe ezinengi lamakhosi amakhulu bezamkhonzisa.\x + 25.14,26.\x*
\v 8 Kuzakuthi-ke isizwe lombuso okungayikumsebenzela yena, uNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni, lokungayikubeka intamo yakho ngaphansi kwejogwe lenkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 27.11,12; 30.8.\x* lesosizwe ngizasijezisa, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngenkemba\x + 14.12; 27.13.\x* langendlala langomatshayabhuqe wesifo, ngize ngikuqede ngesandla sakhe.
\v 9 Lina-ke lingabalaleli abaprofethi benu\x + 27.14,16.\x* labavumisi benu\x + 14.14; 29.8. Dute. 18.10.\x* labaphuphi benu labachasisi bemibono benu\x + Isa. 2.6. Dute. 18.10.\x* labalumbi benu\x + Dute. 18.10.\x* abakhuluma kini besithi: Kaliyikuyisebenzela inkosi yeBhabhiloni.\x + 27.14,16.\x*
\v 10 Ngoba baprofetha amanga kini,\x + 27.14,16.\x*\x + 5.31; 14.14.\x* ukuze balisuse liye khatshana lelizwe lakini, lokuze ngilixotshe liphume, libhubhe.
\v 11 Kodwa isizwe esizangenisa intamo yaso ngaphansi kwejogwe lenkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 27.11,12; 30.8.\x* siyisebenzele, ngizasiyekela elizweni laso, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuthi silisebenze, sihlale kulo.
\p
\v 12 Ngakhuluma lakuZedekhiya inkosi yakoJuda\x + 28.1.\x* njengokwalawomazwi wonke ngathi: Ngenisani intamo zenu ngaphansi kwejogwe lenkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 27.11,12; 30.8.\x* lisebenzele yona labantu bayo, liphile.\x + 27.17; 38.17.\x*
\v 13 Lizafelani, wena labantu bakho,\x + Hez. 18.31.\x* ngenkemba, ngendlala, langomatshayabhuqe wesifo,\x + 14.12; 27.13.\x* njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd* mayelana lesizwe esingayikuyisebenzela inkosi yeBhabhiloni?\x + 27.8.\x*
\v 14 Ngakho lingawalaleli amazwi abaprofethi abakhuluma kini besithi: Kaliyikuyisebenzela inkosi yeBhabhiloni;\x + 27.9.\x* ngoba baprofetha amanga kini.\x + 27.10.\x*
\v 15 Ngoba kangibathumanga, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, kodwa baprofetha amanga ngebizo lami,\x + 14.14.\x* ukuze ngilixotshe,\x + 27.10.\x* libhubhe, lina labaprofethi abaprofetha kini.
\p
\v 16 Ngasengikhuluma kubapristi lakulababantu bonke, ngisithi: Itsho njalo IN\nd kosi\nd*: Lingawalaleli amazwi abaprofethi benu abaprofetha kini besithi:\x + 27.14,16.\x* Khangelani, izitsha zendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* zizabuyiswa khathesi masinyane zivela eBhabhiloni;\x + 28.3. 2 Kho. 24.13. 2 Lan. 36.7,10. Dan. 1.2.\x* ngoba baprofetha amanga kini.\x + 27.14,16.\x*
\v 17 Lingabalaleli; sebenzelani inkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 27.17; 38.17.\x* liphile. Kungani umuzi lo ube lunxiwa?\x + 7.34; 44.2.\x*
\v 18 Kodwa uba bengabaprofethi, njalo uba ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* likubo, khathesi kabayincenge iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla,\x + Jobe 21.15. Isa. 59.16.\x* ukuthi izitsha eziseleyo endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* lendlini yenkosi yakoJuda leJerusalema zingayi eBhabhiloni.\x + Dan. 1.2.\x*
\p
\v 19 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla mayelana lezinsika,\x + 2 Kho. 25.13.\x* langolwandle,\x + 2 Kho. 25.13.\x* langezisekelo,\x + 2 Kho. 25.13.\x* langensali yezitsha ezisele kulumuzi,
\v 20 uNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni angazithathanga, ekuthumbeni kwakhe uJekoniya indodana kaJehoyakhimi inkosi yakoJuda eJerusalema emusa eBhabhiloni,\x + 24.1. Mat. 1.11,12.\x* lazo zonke izikhulu zakoJuda leJerusalema;
\v 21 yebo, itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli mayelana lezitsha eziseleyo endlini kaJehova lendlini yenkosi yakoJuda leJerusalema:
\v 22 Zizasiwa eBhabhiloni,\x + 52.17,20,21. 2 Kho. 25.13. 2 Lan. 36.18.\x* zibe khona kuze kube lusuku\x + 25.12; 32.5.\x* engizakuzihambela ngalo,\x + 29.10.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*; khona ngizazenyusa,\x + Ezra 1.7; 5.14; 7.19.\x* ngizibuyisele kulindawo.\x + 29.10.\x*\x + Ezra 1.7; 5.14; 7.19.\x*